{"tid":42934,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"張曉明何時回港？ 中聯辦法律部部長：對不起，回頭再說","createTime":"2016-12-17T06:08:46.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-17T16:34:14.000Z","uid":5195,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5817a4ed6cfb5e04f48ae5bd7b4847a458df2b7f","tid":42934,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"在特首梁振英宣布放棄連任之後，中聯辦主任張曉明一直未有在港公開露面，更缺席不少獲邀的公開場合，惹來不少揣測。直至昨晚，中央電視台播出張曉明參與中央經濟工作會議的新聞片段，似為失蹤一說闢謠。<br />\n<br />\n中聯辦法律部部長王振民今日出席一個研討會時，被問到張曉明何時回港工作，王振民回應指「對不起，回頭再說。」"},{"pid":"525b8a0a1ada5e11bab40aee8fc0ec76db4db266","tid":42934,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:11:35.000Z","msg":"篤左灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2d3ad860fad3cddeeb5c5394757e9be8039f6ff","tid":42934,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:12:41.000Z","msg":"軟禁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5634eed9e0415a7e6cb7e5c385cc77d6e7303d4b","tid":42934,"uid":35070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T06:14:21.000Z","msg":"張曉明(被消失)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e8816a743372ab97f67a9d114c635103b96c95","tid":42934,"uid":37596,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T07:32:59.000Z","msg":"變左國家機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a94e1ba99e9f4af1ac427fdb9c20d578f1c6b9","tid":42934,"uid":42909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"唔通偉人燒山又講中<br />\n小明一去無回頭"},{"pid":"fcf418afbd7d980e776d45f9cb1a72b71061bb78","tid":42934,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-17T08:48:21.000Z","msg":"小明BB <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img s